@using X.PagedList
@using X.PagedList.Mvc.Core
@using X.PagedList.Web.Common;
@model IPagedList<ECommerce.Models.Product>


    <div class="row">
    @foreach (var product in Model)
    {
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6">
            <div class="row p-2">
                <div class="col-12 p-1" style="border:1px solid #008cba; border-radius: 5px">
                    <div class="card">
                        <img src="@product.ImageUrl" class="card-img-top rounded" style="object-fit: contain; height: 200px" />
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <div class="pl-1">
                                <p class="card-title h5 text-primary">@product.Name</p>
                                    <p class="card-title text-info"><b>@product.Brand</b></p>
                                </div>                          
                                <div class="pl-1">
                                    <h5><b>@product.Price.ToString("C")</b></h5>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <a asp-action="Details" class="btn btn-primary form-control" asp-route-productId="@product.Id">
                                Details
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

    }
    </div>
<div class="row mt-2">
    <div class="col-12">
        <div>
            @if (Model.PageCount> 0){
            <ul class="pagination pagination-lg justify-content-center">
                <li class="page-item @(Model.IsFirstPage ? "disabled" : "")">
                    <a class="page-link" href="@Url.Action("Index", new { page = 1 })">&laquo;</a>
                </li>
                @for (var i = 1; i <= Model.PageCount; i++)
                {
                    <li class="page-item @(i == Model.PageNumber ? "active" : "")">
                        <a class="page-link" href="@Url.Action("Index", new { page = i })">@i</a>
                    </li>
                }
                <li class="page-item @(Model.IsLastPage ? "disabled" : "")">
                    <a class="page-link" href="@Url.Action("Index", new { page = Model.PageCount })">&raquo;</a>
                </li>
                </ul>
            }
            else
            {
                <h1 class="mt-5 text-primary text-center">Produit pas trouvé</h1>
            }
        </div>
    </div>
</div>